title: Crispy Baked Falafel
description: These falafels are golden brown and crispy on the outside. The insides are tender, delicious, and full of fresh herbs.

title: Peanut Soba Noodle Slaw
description: Healthy Asian slaw made with cabbage, carrots and soba noodles, tossed in a bold peanut-sesame sauce.

title: Vegetable Paella
description: Loaded with vegetables, chickpeas, and savory, smoky rice. This Spanish dish is perfect for parties.

title: Sweet Potato Enchiladas
description: The enchiladas are stuffed with creamy, hearty sweet potato, plus black beans, feta cheese, and spices.

title: Thai Red Curry
description: Tastier than takeout and healthier, too. This recipe is vegetarian, vegan and gluten free for all to enjoy.
